<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 22:32:31 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a064d7d09baf</link><description>&lt;p&gt;玛丽亚·麦基与孤独正义乐队在1987年荷兰Pinkpop音乐节。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Maria McKee with Lone Justice at Pinkpop 1987, NL." height="990" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sybrand/6a064d7d09baf.jpg" width="1024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sybrand.some.pics"&gt;@sybrand&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 22:32:31 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>波特兰水边阴天慢跑</title><link>https://some.pics/6a06454f15df6</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在缅因州波特兰沿着水边的一次阴天跑步&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A dramatic, dark cloudy sky stretches over a calm bay dotted with anchored boats and a rugged rocky foreground." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ericmwalk/6a06454f15df6.jpg" width="5712"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ericmwalk.some.pics"&gt;@ericmwalk&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 21:57:40 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>晨跑观日出</title><link>https://some.pics/6a06448af0ac0</link><description>&lt;p&gt;沿着水边跑步看日出，这种感觉真的没谁了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Numerous dark wooden pilings emerge from calm water, reflecting a cloudy sunset with a distant glowing sun." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ericmwalk/6a06448af0ac0.jpg" width="5712"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ericmwalk.some.pics"&gt;@ericmwalk&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 21:54:23 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a0638322f0e2</link><description>&lt;p&gt;欧洲魅力，美式风格。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="European charm, American-style. " height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/duggan/6a0638322f0e2.jpg" width="2268"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://duggan.some.pics"&gt;@duggan&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 21:01:41 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>香水LED广告牌</title><link>https://some.pics/6a061ee85f243</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一张购物街上香水广告牌的照片。黄色圆圈内，一个OS模态覆盖层显示该广告牌是LED屏幕。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="There's a LED ad panel epidemic downtown. Why. " height="620" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/al/6a061ee85f243.jpg" width="827"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://al.some.pics"&gt;@al&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 19:13:46 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>